UID:10005606-1775586600-1775592000@sdlancaster.org
SUMMARY:Community Budget Forum
DESCRIPTION:We invite families to participate in the Community Budget Forum on April 7\, where district leaders will present budget options and be available to answer questions and hear feedback. \nChildcare and interpretation will be provided. While RSVP is not required\, it is strongly encouraged for those planning to attend in person so we can better accommodate all participants. \nThank you for taking the time to stay informed and engaged. We will continue to share updates and resources as decisions are considered in the weeks ahead. \nTo watch the livestream\, visit: https://sdlancaster.org/discover-sdol/leadership/
URL:https://sdlancaster.org/event/community-budget-forum/
LOCATION:LGI Room\, Lincoln Middle School\, 1001 Lehigh Avenue\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
CATEGORIES:Board
END:VEVENT
